<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Zoo Management</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: url('<%= asset_path("background.jpg") %>'); /* Rails asset path for background image */
            background-size: cover; /* makes sure the image covers the entire screen */
            background-position: center; /* Centers the background image:0 */
            background-repeat: no-repeat; /* Prevents the image from repeating */
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); /* put in semi-transparent white background for readability */
            border-radius: 10px; /* : adds rounded corners */
        }
        header {
            background: rgba(0, 128, 0, 0.8); /* Adjusted for transparency over the background image */
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            margin: 0;
        }
        section {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Our Zoo</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <section>
            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>
                At <span class="highlight">Isle Zoo</span>, we are passionate about connecting people with the wonders of wildlife.
                Our mission is to create an educational, fun, and safe environment where visitors can experience the beauty of nature
                while learning about conservation and the importance of protecting our planet's biodiversity.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>
                We strive to be a leading institution in wildlife conservation, research, and education. Through our efforts,
                we aim to inspire a deeper understanding and appreciation of animals and their natural habitats. 
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>What We Offer</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>A wide variety of animal exhibits featuring species from all around the world.</li>
                <li>Interactive educational programs for children and adults.</li>
                <li>Special events and seasonal attractions.</li>
                <li>Behind-the-scenes tours and experiences with our expert zookeepers.</li>
                <li>Community engagement through conservation initiatives and outreach programs.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Our Commitment to Conservation</h2>
            <p>
                Conservation is at the heart of everything we do. We work closely with international and local organizations to
                protect endangered species and their habitats. By visiting our zoo, you directly contribute to these efforts
                and help us make a difference.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Join Us!</h2>
            <p>
                Whether you're visiting for a day of adventure, joining as a member, or supporting our conservation projects,
                you're part of a community that cares deeply about wildlife and our planet. Thank you for helping us make a
                positive impact!
            </p>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
